snippet.title: v8.0 In Search of the Sun Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v8.0 In Search of the Sun coming soon! Durandal's new battlesuit Reign Solaris debuts!
Part 2 Main Story Chapter VII: Bouquets of Unfulfilled Wishes, featured event Countdown: To Sweet Dreams!, and more exciting content to be released! Stay tuned!
Voice Artists:
Erdős Helia: Yui Kondo
Coralie 6626 Planck: Saya Aizawa
Durandal: Mamiko Noto
